<EMEvent>

        <eventDescription>iFlow processing failed: ${property.errorMsg}</eventDescription>
        <eventAttributes>
            <EMEventAttribute>
                <name>BTP-IS MessageId</name>
                <value>${header.SAP_MessageProcessingLogID}</value>
            </EMEventAttribute>
            <EMEventAttribute>
                <name>Cobrainer Job Family Id</name>
                <value>${property.cbrJobFamilyId}</value>
            </EMEventAttribute>
            <EMEventAttribute>
                <name>Error Code</name>
                <value>[SAP-IS_SFSF] ${property.errorCode}</value>
            </EMEventAttribute>
            <EMEventAttribute>
                <name>Message</name>
                <value>${property.errorMsg}</value>
            </EMEventAttribute>
        </eventAttributes>
    </EMEvent>
</EMEvent>
